  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

  <p>Create nested JSON structures by defining object fields:</p>

  <pre set:html={`<code>model User {
  fields {
    id() int
    profile() object
  }

  gens {
    func id() {
      return iter + 1
    }

    func profile() {
      return {
        "firstName": FirstName(),
        "lastName": LastName(),
        "address": {
          "city": City(),
          "country": Country()
        }
      }
    }
  }
}</code>`}></pre>

